data.description: Back to The Market!!!Fantastic East Lancaster Home!! New Interior Paint, Wood floor, are just a few of the nice touches!! Step into this warm inviting home with a formal living room and dining area to your left that led directly into a beautiful kitchen with rich color granite counter tops and dark color cabinets that connect to the family room with a gorgeous white tile fireplace and views right into a large backyard with a covered patio ready for your grill and outdoor entertainment. downstairs laundry room and a 2-car garage with extra storage area. Head up the beautiful staircase to a nice master bedroom and full bathroom, 2 bedrooms and don't forget the spacious RV access area big enough for all your toys. This house will not disappoint!!
